{"tid":231002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救撚 食咩幫助通便","createTime":"2017-05-05T17:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T13:08:41.000Z","uid":77166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97c41350879e3d67a93dbc8d7523c6d522b8da07","tid":231002,"uid":77166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"救命 我無屙屎三日 <br />\n前個排便秘到消化不良 不停嘔同胃脹<br />\n睇醫生話我有入無出開左通便我食<br />\n食完無嘔同胃脹就停食左<br />\n之後就keep住無屎屙<br />\n我本身都無乜屎屙 但唔想谷屎谷死<br />\n尋求解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我已經早餐食蕉同乳酪 keep左3日<br />\n今日一次過食左三條蕉屙得一，二粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇長期食通便藥唔好 認真求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf8ed73ca5f1acc4295adbfca64746267b04bdc","tid":231002,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:39:26.000Z","msg":"老鼠藥"},{"pid":"bef6e9eb31efd516c62bc91e34db380f6226e6fd","tid":231002,"uid":56199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:43:20.000Z","msg":"去藥房買維B食"},{"pid":"5a8e782bbedb599ed44ea81d49586f0197cd3c70","tid":231002,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:46:51.000Z","msg":"食辣野或者龜苓膏<br />\n12小時內屎眼大爆發"},{"pid":"29e32431c130742ea4843b3246266b2a7d35d4ee","tid":231002,"uid":77166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去藥房買維B食</blockquote><br />\n絲打係咪試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪一直要keep住食到身體調理好 我唔想失去自動屙屎呢個功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bad9b357f27ef03b05e7ce3fecfb177de71bf76","tid":231002,"uid":77166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T17:48:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食辣野或者龜苓膏<br />\n12小時內屎眼大爆發</blockquote><br />\n我食辣野會屙 但唔係次次work 長期食辣好辛苦<img src=\"/asset