\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲嚴重過你<br />\n一個月平均痾得4-5次 仲要次次得幾粒仔<br />\n已經日日食菜 生果<br />\n咩辣野咖啡都試曬都冇幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食3條蕉都係屙幾粒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想依賴通便藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8d8e6e26597b02615454a6566c7187f36a3078","tid":231002,"uid":93701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:06:52.000Z","msg":"靚女唔柯屎？"},{"pid":"34218470d71ca7f2bd1ff6f6537bba87bde9c9e5","tid":231002,"uid":77166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靚女唔柯屎？</blockquote><br />\n靚女係唔屙 柒頭係無得屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d078c72e0301264a215c78f6f0a5cf760dfbc9b","tid":231002,"uid":74450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:13:35.000Z","msg":"最近我同你差唔多，胃痛食完藥好返就便秘，<br />\n成個星期都無屎屙，條腸直頭脹到有d痛，最尾用佐一招算係解決佐，<br />\n就係每日起身時就去灌水，飲到頂唔順為止，我就大既500ml，而且要一口氣飲落去，中間唔好停，而且要溫水<br />\n，加少少鹽，飲完隔一陣應該就有便意，我第一日就屙佐少少，之後我連續咁做3日，就正常返。<br />\n而且無十足便意時無謂坐係馬桶，只會增加你的心理壓力。"},{"pid":"f1f7e9b0e5c092eb41aa745adf8d48f568ceaee8","tid":231002,"uid":3146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:13:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去萬寧買包暢便梅 <br />\n痾到你仆街<br />\n<br />\nBtw之前係泰國既屈臣氏買過盒蜜瓜沖劑<br />\n飲完之後痾到七彩 d屎好臭</blockquote><br />\n但長期食得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我怕一唔食無得屙 身體會依賴左佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪去買支西梅汁飲"},{"pid":"ee9739d9f4a21dc2706bb5cb716de392cbf6d0ad","tid":231002,"uid":36849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0